{"type": "article", "id": 28236, "title": "Valentino 度假系列不错，以及，有款包也许你想看看｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-06-15T11:48:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 11718, "name": "印花"}, {"id": 5368, "name": "古巴"}, {"id": 14934, "name": "刺绣"}, {"id": 28997, "name": "民族风"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 28998, "name": "RiRi"}, {"id": 5910, "name": "Stuart Weitzman"}, {"id": 28999, "name": "Edun"}, {"id": 12792, "name": "Neiman Marcus"}, {"id": 18560, "name": "Proenza Schouler"}, {"id": 29000, "name": "Ted Baker"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}, {"id": 17322, "name": "Gigi Hadid"}, {"id": 3264, "name": "山本耀司"}, {"id": 29001, "name": "A$AP Rocky"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170801BX8e0jInc65yuHrh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/judd-crane-ceo-of-proenza-schouler-10455139/\"><b>Judd Crane 担任 Proenza Schouler 新 CEO</b></a>｜ Proenza Schouler 任命 Judd Crane 为新首席执政官，接替去年六月担任过渡时期 CEO 的 Ron Frasch。九月初生效，此前 Crane 是伦敦 Selfridges 女装及配饰部门总监，还担任过连卡佛母公司 Lane Crawford Joyce 集团旗下的配饰部门 Pedder Group 高级采购总监。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionmag.com/news/Retailer-Ted-Baker-revenue-up-on-online-growth-new-stores,703092.html\"><b>Ted Baker 销售额上涨</b></a>｜英国品牌 Ted Baker 近日宣布在截至 6 月 11 日的 19 周内，由于线上销售及新开门店，收益增长了 11.3%／目前全球拥有 465 家门店，销售额增长了 12.7%，电商销售额上涨了 32.3%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/neiman-marcus-sales-10455789/\"><b>Neiman Marcus 百货利润大幅下跌</b></a>｜美国精品百货店 Neiman Marcus 面临挑战，近日财报显示已经连续第三个季度销售额下跌，利润有 81% 的下滑。三季度收益从去年同期的 1980 万美元跌至 380 万美元，总收入从 12.2 亿下跌了 4.2% 至 11.7 亿美元。同店销售额下降 5%。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Rihanna-launches-second-fragrance-from-her-RiRi-collection-Crush-by-Rihanna,703436.html\"><b>Rihanna 发布新香水</b></a>｜Rihanna 周二宣布发布一款新香水 Crush by Rihanna， 这是她个人第八款香水，也是自己同名品牌 RiRi collection 发布的第二款香。Rihanna 自己设计了瓶身，灵感延续了第一款 RiRi 香水。预计今年 8 月上市。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170746hfUIZo1qDcQe906a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61498439\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">很火的法国包袋品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/coteciel-ys-yohji-yamamoto-capsule-collection\"> Côte&amp;Ciel 与山本耀司（Yohji Yamamoto）的成衣品牌 Y’s 合作</a>推出胶囊系列背包，两款将于 6 月 17 日在 Y's 门店上市：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170746S46X71KNlQBscIpn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75473579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707472IfLjboqY5hRim8U.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75473579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170747JYH0UTf1Xo6r9zVP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75473579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/resort-2017/valentino\">Valentino 发布 2017 度假系列</a>，一向很仙的风格增添了更多厚重的色彩、刺绣和热带风情的印花，设计师 Maria Grazia Chiuri 表示灵感源自古巴，并认为古巴的迷人之处在于混合了西班牙、非洲以及 50 年代美国的记忆：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707480MkwUtLzR5BqNEQn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170748wBkbDtymo6CxLjIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170749Z17B6JFtOg0LA8Vq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707507FfV3dlZCAm0yExz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170751wt9WO1FuyzRoKcV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707523UN27t5JD6i1GkIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170752TzfLJ1trdP9HIqM0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707529nZL8FipYHPc1Svb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>饶舌歌手 A$AP Rocky 、电影 Kids 导演Larry Clark、法国新人男演员 Rod Paradot 和模特 Dylan Roques <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/asap-rocky-dior-2016-fw-campaign\">为 Dior Homme 2016 秋冬季拍摄大片</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170753jXDWu6APqQmK9MJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170753ESrpG0w5YPsvzIDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070217075487c5U6Bujn0L91ND.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170754ifq8GBEwR3nJ2s7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/resort-2017/new-york/edun/review/\">Edun 2017 度假系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170755mJ7BKSEVaD3jfs1y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170755AE1u6wZWSF2DyiHr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170756K6qS7xEXfAcsVHhY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021707573TScaItPnKXu6pRE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170757okXbxaDNMZfJ7VCq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170758NcmAvfyCQ2uKpnGa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170758K4xumMTrL7bPCdXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/gigi-hadid-featured-stuart-weitzman-fall-2016-campaign-10455695/\">Gigi Hadid 为 Stuart Weitzman 拍摄秋季大片</a>，她和另两位超模 Joan Smalls、Lily Aldridge 全裸出镜拍摄了这一品牌的春季大片，此次单人回归：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170759yABWeqVQhL1urgJ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170759FeqNCMI507xsVuog.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">日本知名百货 BEAMS 40 周年庆已联合多个品牌推出特别款，最新是与 New Balance 合作发布了采用优质小羊皮制作的 1400 鞋款：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170800wUeCxWRE15ZobhlV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170800WIcsqGb1QpF6mNow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}